::Q1::Which method cuts all network at the browser level? {=context.setOffline(true) ~page.route ~Network.emulateNetworkConditions}
::Q2::Which mechanism allows granular per-endpoint control? {=page.route ~context.setOffline ~browser.newContext}
::Q3::Which mode does route.abort('failed') simulate? {=Network error ~Slow response ~Offline mode}
::Q4::Which Playwright tool simulates full-bandwidth throttling? {=CDP Network.emulateNetworkConditions ~page.route delay ~context.setOffline}
::Q5::Which method is ideal for offline PWA cache verification? {=context.setOffline(true) ~route.abort ~route.fulfill}
::Q6::Which route approach simulates slow API responses? {=Delayed fulfill/continue ~abort('failed') ~CDP offline}
::Q7::Which file types are commonly blocked to test performance? {=Images ~HTML ~JSON}
::Q8::Which resource category is used for web fonts? {=font ~media ~manifest}
::Q9::Which method blocks all third‑party domains? {=page.route(pattern, abort) ~context.setOffline ~route.continue}
::Q10::Which condition simulates realistic variable latency? {=jittered delay ~static delay ~instant fulfill}
::Q11::Which CDP profile simulates approx. 1.5 Mbps down? {=3G ~slow‑2g ~fast‑3g}
::Q12::Which mode is best to test timeout behaviour? {=route.delay + abort('timedout') ~CDP offline ~asset blocking}
::Q13::Which test ensures layout remains intact without images? {=placeholder image mocking ~font blocking ~CDP throttle}
::Q14::Which method blocks fonts from CDNs? {=page.route(/fonts/, abort) ~context.setOffline ~route.fallback}
::Q15::Which operation clears service‑worker cache? {=caches.delete() ~localStorage.clear ~context.setOffline(false)}
::Q16::Which fixture delays all /api/** calls? {=slowNetwork fixture ~offline fixture ~noAssets fixture}
::Q17::Which fixture blocks images, fonts, and media? {=noAssets ~offline ~slowNetwork}
::Q18::Which technique simulates bandwidth-constrained downloads? {=CDP throughput limits ~abort images ~offline mode}
::Q19::Which scenario tests optimistic UI behaviour? {=Offline queue sync ~PWA cache load ~Slow 3G first render}
::Q20::Which principle ensures stable tests without animations? {=Inject no‑animation CSS ~Throttle network ~Block third parties}